\c 27
\s Vakuru vehondo
\p
\v 1 Zvino vana vaIsraeri neuwandu hwavo, misoro yemadzibaba, nevakuru vezvuru nevemazana, nevatariri vavo vaishandira mambo pazvinhu zvese zvemapoka aipinda nekubuda mwedzi nemwedzi pamwedzi yese yegore, boka rimwe nerimwe; zvuru makumi maviri nezvina.
\v 2 Pamusoro peboka rekutanga pamwedzi wekutanga, Jashobheyami mwanakomana waZabhadhiyeri; paboka rake paiva nezvuru makumi maviri nezvina.
\v 3 Waiva umwe wevana VaPerezi, musoro wemachinda ehondo pamwedzi wekutanga.
\v 4 Zvino pamusoro peboka remwedzi wechipiri paiva naDhodhayi muAhohi, nepaboka rake; Mikiroti waivawo mutungamiriri; uye paboka rake paiva nezvuru makumi maviri nezvina.
\v 5 Musoro wehondo yetatu pamwedzi wetatu waiva Bhenaya mwanakomana waJehoyadha mupristi mukuru; uye paboka rake paiva nezvuru makumi maviri nezvina.
\v 6 Uyu Bhenaya waiva uya wesimba pavane makumi matatu uye boka rake nderaAmizabhadhi mwanakomana wake.
\v 7 Wechina pamwedzi wechina waiva Asaheri munin'ina waJoabhu, naZebhedhia mwanakomana wake waimutevera; uye paboka rake paiva nezvuru makumi maviri nezvina.
\v 8 Weshanu pamwedzi weshanu waiva muchinda Shamhuti mulzira; uye boka rake raiva nezvuru makumi maviri nezvina.
\v 9 Wetanhatu pamwedzi wetanhatu waiva Ira mwanakomana waIkeshi muTekowa; paboka rake paiva nezvuru makumi maviri nezvina.
\v 10 Wechinomwe pamwedzi wechinomwe waiva Herezi muPeroni wevanakomana vaEfuremu; paboka rake paiva nezvuru makumi maviri nezvina.
\v 11 Wesere pamwedzi wesere waiva Shebhekai muHushati, wevaZerihi; paboka rake paiva nezvuru makumi maviri nezvina.
\v 12 Wepfumbamwe pamwedzi wepfumbamwe waiva Abhiezeri muAnatoti wevaBhenjamini; paboka rake paiva nezvuru makumi maviri nezvina.
\v 13 Wegumi pamwedzi wegumi waiva Maharai muNetofati wevaZerihi; paboka rake paiva nezvuru makumi maviri nezvina.
\v 14 Wegumi neumwe pamwedzi wegumi neumwe waiva Bhenaya muPiratoni wevana vaEfuremu; paboka rake paiva nezvuru makumi maviri nezvina.
\v 15 Wgumi nevaviri pamwedzi wegumi nemiviri, waiva Heridhai muNetofati waOtiniyeri; paboka rake pakange pane zvuru zvina makumi maviri nezvina.
\s Varairi vemarudzi gumi nemaviri
\p
\v 16 Uye pamusoro pemarudzi aIsraeri: Mutongi weVaRubheni waiva Eriezeri mwanakomana waZikiri. UuVaSimioni; Shefatiya mwanakomana waMaaka.
\v 17 KuVaRevhi; Hashabhiya, mwanakomana waKemueri; kuVaAroni; Zadhoki.
\v 18 KuVaJudha; Erihu pavanin'ina vaDhavhidhi. Kuna Isasikari; Omiri mwanakomana waMikayeri.
\v 19 Kuna Zebhuruni: Ishimaya mwanakomana waObhadhiya. Kuna Nafutari; Jeremoti mwanakomana waAziyeri.
\v 20 Kuvana vaEfuremu; Hosheya mwanakomana waAzaziya. Kuhafu yerudzi rwaManase; Joweri mwanakomana waPedhaya.
\v 21 Kuhafu yerudzi rwaManase paGiriyadhi, Idho mwanakomana waZekariya. Kuna Bhenjamini; Jasiyeri mwanakomana waAbhineri.
\v 22 Kuna Dhani; Azareri mwanakomana waJehorami. Ndivo vaiva vakuru vemarudzi aIsraeri.
\p
\v 23 Asi Dhavhidhi haana kutora uwandu hwevane makore makumi maviri nepasi; nokuti Jehovha waiva ati achawanza VaIsraeri senyeredzi dzekumatenga.
\v 24 Joabhu mwanakomana waZeruya akatanga kuverenga, asi haana kupedza; kutsamwa kwaJehovha kukamukira VaIsraeri nemhosva iyi; uye havana kuisa kuwanda kwavo pamakoronike amambo Dhavhidhi.
\s Vamwe varanda vaDhavhidhi
\p
\v 25 Mutariri wefuma yamambo akange ari Azimavheti mwanakomana waAdhieri mutariri wefuma yapaminda, napamaguta, napamisha, neyapanhare, akange ari Jonatani mwanakomana waUziya;
\v 26 mutariri wavanhu vaibata paminda vachirima pasi, akange ari Eziri mwanakomana waKerubhi.
\v 27 Mutariri weminda yemizambiringa, akange ari Shimei muRamati; mutariri wezvibereko zveminda yemizambiringa, wedzimba dzewaini, akange ari Zabhadhi muShifimi;
\v 28 mutariri wemiorivhi nemionde yakange iri pamapani, akange ari Bhaari-Hanani muGedheri; mutariri wedzimba dzamafuta akange ari Joashi.
\v 29 Mutariri wamapoka ezvipfuwo, zvaifura paSharoni, akange ari Shitirai muSharoni, uye mutariri wamapoka aigara pamipata, akange ari Shafati mwanakomana waAdhirai;
\v 30 mutariri wamakamera akange ari Obhiri muIshimaeri, uye mutariri wembongoro akange ari Jedheiya muMeronoti;
\v 31 mutariri wamapoka amakwai akange ari Jazizi muHagiri. Ava vese vakange vari vatariri venhumbi dzamambo Dhavhidhi.
\v 32 Uye Jonatani muzukuru waDhavhidhi akange ari gurukota, murume akangwara, munyori; Jehieri mwanakomana waHakimoni aigara navanakomana vamambo;
\v 33 Ahitoferi akange ari gurukota ramambo; naHushai muAriki yaiva shamwari yamambo;
\v 34 aitevera Ahitoferi ndiJehoyadha mwanakomana waBhenaya, naAbhiyatari; mukuru wehondo yamambo akange ari Joabhu.
